Package com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter

Class MultiCriteriaObjectArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter.SimpleCriteria
      • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter.MultiCriteriaObject
        • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.filter.MultiCriteriaObjectArray
  • public class MultiCriteriaObjectArray
extends MultiCriteriaObject
    An array of MultiCriteriaObjects. This generates a JSON object containing an array of MultiCriteriaObjects. The following is an example of filter JSON syntax this object generates: 
     ?criteria={"credentials":[{"type":"bannerId","value":"myBannerId"}]}
    See SimpleCriteria.Builder.withMultiCriteriaObjectArray(String) for how to build this object.
    Since:
    0.2.0
    Author:
    David Kumar
